title: Burt's Bees Rosewater Toner 8oz
description: Tone your skin naturally with Burt’s Bees® Rosewater Toner. Natural rosewater, known for its mild astringent properties and simply beautiful aroma, combines with aloe vera and glycerin in this gentle skin toner to remove lingering traces of dirt, oil and make-up. This 99.9% natural facial toner leaves your face feeling refreshed and is gentle enough to use every day. After applying toner, follow with your favorite Burt’s Bees® face cream or lotion. Put the power of nature to work for your skin with Burt’s Bees.
